HUMANITARIAN USE NOTICE:

This software is specifically intended for humanitarian purposes, including but
not limited to crisis communication, disaster response, and emergency situations.

The authors encourage use of this software to help people in need, especially
in situations where traditional communication infrastructure has failed or is
unavailable.

Special permission is granted to humanitarian organizations, NGOs, and rescue
services to use this software without restriction in emergency situations.
